    {
      "Schema": "document",
      "Type": "CtVPreferences",
      "Field": "PageMode",
      "Docs": [
        {
          "Kind": "Description",
          "Text": "窗口模式，可取值如下：\nNone——常规模式\nFullScreen——打开后全文显示\nUseOutlines——同时呈现文档大纲\nUseThumbs——同时呈现缩略图\nUseCustomTags——同时呈现语义结构\nUseLayers——同时呈现图层\nUseAttachments——同时呈现附件\nUseBookmarks——同时呈现书签\n默认值为 None。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "Schema": "document",
      "Type": "CtVPreferences",
      "Field": "PageLayout",
      "Docs": [
        {
          "Kind": "Description",
          "Text": "页面布局模式，可取值如下：\nOnePage——单页模式\nOneColumn——单列模式\nTwoPageL——对开模式\nTwoColumnL——对开连续模式\nTwoPageR——对开靠右模式\nTwoColumnR——对开连续靠右模式\n默认值为 OneColumn。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "Schema": "document",
      "Type": "CtVPreferences",
      "Field": "TabDisplay",
      "Docs": [
        {
          "Kind": "Description",
          "Text": "标题栏显示模式，可取值如下：\nFileName——文件名称\nDocTitle——呈现元数据中的 Title 属性\n默认值为 FileName。当设置为 DocTitle 但不存在 Title 属性时，按照 FileName 处理。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "Schema": "document",
